<div id="documentation" class="py-lg-5">
    <div class="container-fluid py-3">
        <div class="container px-4 fs-6">
            <h4 id="library_website_instructions" class="fs-3 text-center mb-4">Library Website Instructions</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Go to link <a href="https://cvsutanzalibrary.site/">https://cvsutanzalibrary.site/</a></li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Home</button> to see the OPAC and to view announcements, events, and library information in Cavite State University Tanza Campus library.</li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Books</button> to view all books in CvSU Tanza Campus library.</li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Services</button> to view all services in CvSU Tanza Campus library.</li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Acquisitions</button> to view newly acquired books according to the year they arrived at CvSU Tanza Campus library.</li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-top">Feedback</button> located at the right side of the screen to provide feedback about the library website or physical library.</li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-top">Chat</button> to ask a question or read FAQs about the website, and AI replies to you immediately.</li>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Login</button> and use CvSU mail to enter the website's other features like requesting reservations to borrow a book and tracking own book circulations.</li>
            </ol>

            <h4 id="login_using_CvSU_mail" class="pt-5"><br>Login using CvSU Mail</h4>

            <ol>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Login</button> .</li>
                <p>For the first time login:</p>
                <ol type="a">
                    <li>Click <button class="btn btn-white border-black border-1 shadow-sm fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill"> Continue with Google</button> and use your CvSU mail.</li>
                    <li>Select your member type (Student or Faculty staff).</li>
                    <li>Complete information such as login credentials and user important details and answer the form correctly and precisely because users can only answer the form once.</li>
                    <li>Redirect to the profile page.</li>
                </ol>
                <p>Next time login:</p>
                <ol type="a">
                    <li>Enter login credentials or click <button class="btn btn-white border-black border-1 shadow-sm fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill"> Continue with Google</button> and use your CvSU mail.</li>
                    <li>Redirect to the profile page.</li>
                </ol>
            </ol>
            <h4 id="requesting_reservation_for_borrowing_books" class="pt-5"><br>Requesting Reservation for Borrowing Books</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Click <button class="btn btn-primary fs-7 py-1 rounded-pill">Books</button> to view all books and select books you want to borrow. Users can only borrow books in general circulations (books with more than 2 copies) while if the book is not available to bring home, the action buttons are <button id='request_btn' class='btn btn-outline-secondary fs-10 p-1' style='white-space: nowrap'>ROOM USE ONLY</button> or <button id='request_btn' class='btn btn-outline-secondary fs-10 p-1' style='white-space: nowrap'>BORROWED</button>.</li>
                <li>Click <button class='btn btn-outline-primary fs-10 p-1'><i class='fa-solid fa-upload fa-sm'></i><span class='ps-1'>BORROW</span></button> next to the selected desired book.</li>
                <li>Select the borrowing period from the pickup date and return date.</li>
                <li>Check the <input class="form-check-input me-1 border border-secondary" type="checkbox" value="" required>to make sure that the user has read and agreed to the privacy statement.</li>
                <li>View the Book reservation receipt and click <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill py-1 mx-auto fs-7">SUBMIT</button> to submit the book reservation.</li>
                <li>Users have an option to screenshot or use buttons to <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill fs-7 py-1">Download</button> or <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill fs-7 py-1">Print</button> the receipt and they need to present it with the School ID to campus librarian.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>